OL,7,FGrant Shapps, who was Transport
OL,8,FMinister, accused P&O of behaving like
OL,9,F"pirates of the high sea" and pledged
OL,10,Fto compel the company to pay UK
OL,11,Fminimum wage, which is #10.42 an hour
OL,12,Fand will rise to #11.44 an hour next
OL,13,Fmonth.
OL,15,FBut while the Seafarers' Wages Act
OL,16,Fbecame law last year, the secondary
OL,17,Flegislation that is necessary to
OL,18,Fimplement it has not yet been laid.
