OL,7,FITV News and The Guardian have seen
OL,8,Fcontracts and payslips from between
OL,9,FDecember 2023 and March 2024, which
OL,10,Fshow that P&O is still paying some
OL,11,Fcrew less than #5 an hour.
OL,13,FTo find out what it's like to work
OL,14,Fonboard a P&O ferry, we posed as
OL,15,Fpassengers and filmed undercover on
OL,16,Fthe company's three ships, which
OL,17,Foperate non-stop across the English
OL,18,FChannel between Dover and Calais.
OL,20,FWe spoke to more than a dozen crew
OL,21,Fwhose identities we are protecting.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/21
