OL,7,FAll of them told us they routinely
OL,8,Fwork 12 hour shifts, seven days a
OL,9,Fweek, for up to 17 weeks at a time,
OL,10,Fwithout a day off and without
OL,11,Fpermission to leave the ship
OL,13,F"It's the same place, the same people,
OL,14,Fyou cannot go outside," one crew
OL,15,Fmember told us. "You go crazy. Every
OL,16,Fday it's sleep, work. Sleep, work.
OL,17,FThat's it".
OL,19,FOne crew member said the experience
OL,20,Fwas "like (being in) a jail".
