OL,7,FThe documents we examined were from
OL,8,Fworkers from developing countries. The
OL,9,Fcrew were employed by PhilCrew
OL,10,FManagement, a recruitment agency based
OL,11,Fin Malta.
OL,13,FThe average hourly rate was #4.87 an
OL,14,Fhour.
OL,16,FP&O hires crew from a variety of
OL,17,Fcountries, including India,
OL,18,FPhilippines, Indonesia, Honduras,
OL,19,FMauritius, Malaysia, Georgia, Serbia,
OL,20,FLatvia, Russia and Ukraine.
