OL,7,FMany crew told us they found it
OL,8,Fexhausting to work 84 hour weeks for
OL,9,Fseveral months at a time and that they
OL,10,Fmissed their families.
OL,12,FBut many also said the rates of pay on
OL,13,Foffer at P&O were better than those on
OL,14,Fother international cruise or cargo
OL,15,Fships they had worked on.
OL,17,F"(In my country) you cannot find a
OL,18,Fsalary like this," one said.
