OL,7,F"You need to work," another crew
OL,8,Fmember confided. "When you have a
OL,9,Ffamily, you need to work".
OL,11,FAs it stands, P&O's conduct is
OL,12,Fentirely legal.
OL,14,FThe company is exploiting a gap in the
OL,15,Flaw that means it is not required to
OL,16,Fpay the minimum wage to seafarers who
OL,17,Fwork on foreign-registered ships that
OL,18,Fsail in international waters and are
OL,19,Femployed by agencies outside the UK.
