OL,7,FOn April 27, 2022, Mr Shapps told the
OL,8,FCommons Transport Select Committee P&O
OL,9,FFerries would need to do three things
OL,10,F"to get out of this mess": pay its
OL,11,Fcrew the UK minimum wage; give back
OL,12,Fthe #11 million of furlough money it
OL,13,Freceived from the government during
OL,14,Fthe pandemic and sack Mr Hebblethwaite.
OL,16,FAs yet, none of these things has
OL,17,Fhappened.
