OL,7,FMr Shapps also pledged to review
OL,8,Fgovernment contracts with P&O and its
OL,9,Fowner DP World. He also ordered the
OL,10,FInsolvency Service to investigate the
OL,11,Factions of both the company and its
OL,12,Fdirectors "as a matter of urgency".
OL,14,FA parliamentary question by Labour has
OL,15,Fsince revealed that the government has
OL,16,Fpaid $291 million (approximately #228
OL,17,Fmillion) to both companies since the
OL,18,Fdismissals.
