OL,7,FP&O Ferries said it needed to sack its
OL,8,Fcrews because the business was on the
OL,9,Fverge of bankruptcy and needed to cut
OL,10,Fits costs.
OL,12,FIndustry insiders tell us that by
OL,13,Fdramatically reducing its wage bill,
OL,14,FP&O has also been able to lower its
OL,15,Fprices and gain a competitive
OL,16,Fadvantage over its rivals.
OL,18,FIn 2023, P&O's freight and passenger
OL,19,Ftraffic increased sharply between
OL,20,FDover and Calais - the UK's busiest
OL,21,Fferry route.
