OL,7,FAccording to data from Freightstat,
OL,8,FP&O won business from the ferry
OL,9,Foperator DFDS and Eurotunnel - both
OL,10,Fcompanies which pay the UK minimum
OL,11,Fwage.
OL,13,FP&O told us the company is "now on
OL,14,Ftrack to be profitable". The company's
OL,15,Faccounts for the year ending December
OL,16,F2022 are more than two months overdue
